deck: Justine was resurrected to become God's assassin. From this she gained powers, but also was left to fight the demon hordes.
description:
Origin

Justine was a fun-loving Swedish orphan living in Medieval Italy. She was a rebel teen who once was a non-believer. After she was murdered by knights in the Pope's service, she was 'drafted' by God to be his assassin as a member of the Fallen.

Major Story Arcs

Lost Souls

In the 11th century, Justine is battling the Unholy in the Vatican City, when she is suddenly teleported to Tibet to join the ranks of Pandora, Gatekeeper, Satasha, Lady Death and War Angel in order to stop the Unholy. The Unholy have summoned Lord Sinner and released the Seven Deadly Sins from Pandora's Box. An uneasy alliance is formed between the women, long enough for them to defeat the demons and lock the Seven Deadly Sins back in Pandora's Box.
name: Justine
